 cookie.Domain = "https://contoso.com";
 new CookieContainer().Add(cookie);
 ``` 
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fd87-142">Viene utilizzato il carattere virgola come delimitatore tra cookie distinti nella stessa riga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fd87-142">The comma character is used as a delimiter between separate cookies on the same line.</span></span>

  
  
